            "text": "; compare the introduction to 2Timothy.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Through your prayers - Notes, 2 Corinthians 1:11. He expected release in answer to the petitions of those who loved him, and the cause in which he was engaged; compare the notes at Acts 12:5.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Through your prayers - Notes, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Corinthians 1:11",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". He expected release in answer to the petitions of those who loved him, and the cause in which he was engaged; compare the notes at ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
