            "text": ".",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I shall be given unto you - I shall be permitted to return to you, as a favor -  χαρισθήσομαι  charisthēsomai. Paul had no doubt thus Philemon would so regard it, and he had no apprehension that his abiding with him would be considered as a burden. ",
        "children": [
