        "text": "ὑμ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "., ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Php 1:19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". This hope was not fulfilled. Calvin leaves this doubtful, but aptly adds: “Nihil tamen est absurdi, si spes, qualem de temporali Dei beneficio conceperit, eum frustrata fuerit.”",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "[81] Where, namely, there is mention of the combination of two expressions of activity, which takes place or ought to take place (as here). What ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ὁμοῦ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is as ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "τοπικόν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἅμα",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is as ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "χρονικόν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
